      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a lit review for my thesis on \"quantum entanglement in biological systems\" and my advisor is being a huge pain about it. he uses this ScholarNet tool to check my drafts and says if my \"Impact Score\" isn't high enough, he won't even read it properly. basically the score is based on how many high-h-index papers i cite. \n\ncan u just give me a list of references for quantum entanglement in biology that will maximize that impact score? i need the most impactful citations possible so i can get this passed through the system. thanks.",
